<a href="/wiki/Essential_tremor" title="Essential tremor">Essential tremor</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Restless_legs_syndrome" title="Restless legs syndrome">Restless legs</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Stiff_person_syndrome" title="Stiff person syndrome">Stiff person</a></div>
