</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><i>preformed:</i> <a href="/wiki/Granule_(cell_biology)" title="Granule (cell biology)">Lysosome granules</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <i><a href="/wiki/Vasoactive_amine" title="Vasoactive amine" class="mw-redirect">vasoactive amines</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/Histamine" title="Histamine">Histamine</a>, <a href="/wiki/Serotonin" title="Serotonin">Serotonin</a>)<br />
<i>synthesized on demand:</i> <i><a href="/wiki/Cytokine" title="Cytokine">cytokines</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/Interferon_gamma" title="Interferon gamma" class="mw-redirect">IFN-γ</a>, <a href="/wiki/Interleukin_8" title="Interleukin 8">IL-8</a>, <a href="/wiki/Tumor_necrosis_factor-alpha" title="Tumor necrosis factor-alpha">TNF-α</a>, <a href="/wiki/Interleukin_1" title="Interleukin 1">IL-1</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <i><a href="/wiki/Eicosanoid" title="Eicosanoid">eicosanoids</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/Leukotriene_B4" title="Leukotriene B4">Leukotriene B4</a>, <a href="/wiki/Prostaglandin" title="Prostaglandin">Prostaglandins</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Nitric_oxide" title="Nitric oxide">Nitric oxide</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kinin" title="Kinin">Kinins</a></div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
